@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Update button;
|System|
: (2) Display form to update Branch;
|User|
repeat: (2) Input branch information;
: (3) Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: (4) Validate new information;
backward: (5) Show error message;
repeat while (Information Valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: (6) Update Branch Information;
: (7) Update Manage Branch screen;
stop
@enduml